Olkilikuai le Sedekia


1   Ele rorei oewuo enetii Yeremia eing'uaa Olaitoriani, teina kata apa egilunore Nebukadresa olaiguanani le Babilon o enjore enye pooki o nkitoriat pooki e nkop naatii abori enkitoria enye o ltung'ana pooki le Yerusalem o nkanas enyena pooki ejo: 
2  “Nji ejo Olaitoriani, Enkai e Israel: Shomo irorie Sedekia olaiguanani le Yuda nijoki ninye, ‘Nji ejo Olaitoriani, ng'ura kaishooyo nanu ena anasa apik atua nkaik o laiguanani le Babilon, naa kepejoo ninye te nkima. 
3  Mijeu iyie te nkaina enye, kake meeta nchere mikimbung'i nikiyauni aapik atua enkaina enye; ingurara intae too nkonyek o le Babilon nirorie ninye inchororo nkomomi, naa ilo iyie Babilon.’ 
4  Ore ake eyia toning'o ororei lo Laitoriani, Iyie Sedekia olaiguanani le Yuda! Nji ejo Olaitoriani tialo iyie: ‘Miye iyie to lalem. 
5  Te seriani iyie ilo aye.’ Naa ore apa anaa enatapejoki enkorropil too loo papaai lino, lelo aiguanak apa ootii te dukuya iyie, neijia kipuoi aaiko aapejoki enkorropil, nikinchiraki iyie, ejo, “Aha, Olaitoriani!” ’ Amu airoro nanu, Olaitoriani ojo.”


6  Neitoki Yeremia oloiboni le Nkai aliki kulo rorei pooki Sedekia olaiguanani le Yuda, tiatua Yerusalem ejo, 
7  ina kata apa earare enjore o laiguanani le Babilon Yerusalem o nena anas pooki e Yuda naatelekutua, Lakish o Aseka amu kuna apake nkanas e Yuda naasheta isunta naatelekutua sunta.

Nkiaasin e lejare oo irrindiki


8  Ele rorei oewuo enetii Yeremia eing'uaa Olaitoriani, eidipa olaiguanani Sedekia aitobira olning'o tenebo iltung'ana pooki tiatua Yerusalem pee eibalie elakunoto te ninche, 
9  nchere pee elaku pooki ng'ae Ilhebrania rrindik lenyena olee o eng'oruoi, metaa metii hoo obo oitaa Olyahudi olalashe lenye orrindik. 
10  Nening ninche, lelo kituaak pooki o ltung'ana pooki ooibung'akinote olning'o nchere pee elaaya pooki ng'ae orrindik lenye olee aashu eng'oruoi meitokini aaigil aairrindikishore; neiruk ninche nelaaya ninche. 
11  Kake ore te siadi neibelekenya ninche neitoki aarriny ilewa o nkituaak rrindiki apa ootang'asa aalaaya, neitoki aasishore ninche anaa rrindiki. 
12  Eewuo ororei lo Laitoriani enetii Yeremia eing'uaa Olaitoriani ejo: 
13  “Nji ejo Olaitoriani Enkai e Israel: Aitobira apa nanu olning'o tenebo loo papaai linyi ina kata apa pee aitupuku nanu ninche aitung'uaa enkop e Misiri, aitung'uaa enkaji e sinkaisho, ajo, 
14   ‘Ore te siadi oo larin ile nelaaya ake pooki ng'ae te ntae o Iheburaniai alashe lenye apa likitimirakaki iyie nikisiaaia ninye ilarin ile; meeta nchere pee milaaya ninye aaitung'uaa enkisiaayiare ino;’ kake eitu apa aainining loo papaai lino aashu aaisho nanu nkiyiaa enye. 
15  Irridutua oshi det niasiasa esidai too nkonyek aainei te nkibalunoto e lakunoto, oltung'ani ake o to le latia enye, nintayuyu intae olning'o te dukuya nanu tiatua ina aji naipotieki enkarna ai; 
16  kake inyaakita intae aaibelekenya nisarkionienie enkarna ai ina kata apa erriny pooki ng'ae irrindiki lenyena olee o eng'oruoi, apa nitalaaitie te risioroto e yieunoto enye, niyauwu ninche aaisiaaishore anaa irrindik linyi. 
17  Neaku, nji ejo Olaitoriani: Eitu nanu kining'ining'i teina kibalunoto o elakunoto, pooki ng'ae to lalashe lenye o to lelatia enye; ng'ura, aibalunye nanu te ntae elakunoto to lalem o to lmeitai o to lameyu Olaitoriani ojo. Kaitaa nanu intae enkuretisho too nkitoriat pooki enkop. 
18  Ore lelo tung'ana ootigila olning'o lai lo sotua leitu eibung nkitanapat olning'o lai lo sotua oitobira ninche te dukuya nanu, kaitaas nanu ninche anaa oloshi ashe odung'i aaiper kat are neimi erishata nena rubat. 
19  Ilkituaak le Yuda, o ilkituaak le Yerusalem o sunaishi oogelema, o ilapolosak o ltung'ana pooki leina kop ooima erishata oo matuan eilo ashe 
20  naa kaishooyo nanu ninche apik atua enkaina oo lmang'ati lenye o atua enkaina e lelo ooing'oru enkishui enye. Ore mpopoki enye naa keaku endaa too motonyi o loing'ang'e o ng'uesi enkop. 
21  Ore Sedekia olaiguanani le Yuda, olkituaak lenyena kaishooyo nanu ninche apik atua enkaina oo lmang'ati lenye o atua enkaina oo lmang'ati ooing'oru enkishui enye, atua ena jore o laiguanani le Babilon nikitorrinye aaing'uaa iyie. 
22  Ng'ura kaitanap nanu, Olaitoriani ojo, nashuku nanu ninche meetu ena anasa, nepuonu aagilunore ninye; neya ninye, nepejoo ninye te nkima, kaitaa nanu nkanas e Yuda olmuaate lememanya toki.

